                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="background:rgba(255,107,43,0.08);border-left:3px solid var(--sun);padding:1rem;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin:1rem 0;">
                📌 Victoria Falls (on the Zambezi) is one of the Seven Natural Wonders of the World — and it borders Zimbabwe and Zambia!
              </div>
            `
          }
        ]
      },
      biology: {
        name: 'Biology', icon: '🧬', badge: 'Sciences',
